/installation/jar/.title: Installation from jar.
/installation/jar/.content:
jelu can run from jar :

warning

jelu needs least java 11

  • download github releases section dedicated folder
  • go this folder
  • start ( spring fat dependencies are included) : eg
java jar jelu0170jar
  • want tweak default config (see src/main/resources/applicationyml repo example) just create yaml file called applicationyml same folder jar
example database located next (instead being ${userhome}/jelu/database/ folder) :

jelu:
 databasepath:
automatic metadata online search provided moment through calibre tool fetchebookmetadata

use with install provide path executable config like atrule">metadatacalibreebookmetadatathen open web ui your browser localhost:11111
